s to better help the guild.<br>
<br>
Since the latest change in the requirements raises the bar to 63rd level, I am going to focus on leveling and go on a hiatus for raiding until I meet the AxS requirements again.  I hope that you will all understand that, while I play the game to see new things and raid with you all, meeting the requirements of AxS will have to take precedent over that for a small while.<br>
<br>
